UPDATE contracts SET "extractedText" = 'This Service Agreement is entered into as of January 1 2025 between Acme Corp Client and TechVendor Inc Vendor. Client may terminate this Agreement immediately at any time without cause and without notice. Vendor may only terminate with 180 days written notice. Upon termination Vendor forfeits all unpaid invoices. Vendors total liability shall not exceed 100 dollars. Client may seek unlimited damages from Vendor for any breach. Vendor shall indemnify Client against all claims losses damages and expenses. All work product created by Vendor shall be sole property of Client. Vendor assigns all intellectual property rights to Client including pre-existing tools. Client shall pay Vendor within 90 days of invoice. Late payments incur interest at 5 percent per month. Vendor may suspend services immediately upon non-payment. All disputes resolved by binding arbitration in Clients jurisdiction. Vendor waives right to jury trial and class action. Any legal action must be filed within 30 days of dispute arising.', status = 'analyzed' WHERE id = '99a1dbcf-41c1-4408-93a7-db2f5acd12c1';